@startuml
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam defaultFontName Arial
skinparam defaultFontSize 11

title Operators des Tolerations: Equal vs Exists

rectangle "**Operator: Equal**\nCorrespondance exacte" as equal #B3D9FF {

  rectangle "Taint sur Node" as eq_taint #FFB3B3 {
    label "key: **gpu**\nvalue: **nvidia**\neffect: NoSchedule" as eq_t1
  }

  rectangle "Toleration Pod" as eq_tol #B3FFB3 {
    label "key: **gpu**\noperator: **Equal**\nvalue: **nvidia**\neffect: NoSchedule" as eq_p1
  }

  eq_taint <--> eq_tol : **MATCH**\nkey + value + effect
}

note bottom of equal
  **Utilisation:**
  - Correspondance **precise**
  - value doit etre **identique**

  **Exemple:** Pods GPU specifiques
end note

rectangle "**Operator: Exists**\nCorrespondance flexible" as exists #FFE4B3 {

  rectangle "Taints sur Node" as ex_taint #FFB3B3 {
    label "key: **env**\nvalue: **prod**" as ex_t1
    label "key: **env**\nvalue: **staging**" as ex_t2
    label "key: **env**\nvalue: **dev**" as ex_t3
  }

  rectangle "Toleration Pod" as ex_tol #B3FFB3 {
    label "key: **env**\noperator: **Exists**\neffect: NoSchedule" as ex_p1
  }

  ex_t1 <-- ex_tol : MATCH
  ex_t2 <-- ex_tol : MATCH
  ex_t3 <-- ex_tol : MATCH
}

note bottom of exists
  **Utilisation:**
  - Tolere **n'importe quelle valeur**
  - Wildcard sur la value

  **Exemple:** Tous les envs
end note

rectangle "**Wildcard Total**\nTolere tout" as wildcard #E0E0E0 {
  rectangle "Toleration" as wc_tol #B3FFB3 {
    label "operator: **Exists**\n(pas de key)" as wc_p1
  }

  note right of wc_tol
    Tolere **TOUS** les taints!
    A utiliser avec precaution
  end note
}

@enduml
